---
import BaseLayout from '../../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Breadcrumbs from '../../../../components/Breadcrumbs.astro';
import CTAButton from '../../../../components/CTAButton.astro';
import { COMPANY_INFO } from '../../../../utils/constants';

const lang = 'en';
const post = {
  title: 'Prime Mover Package 2026: 10 Units Fleet Financing Deal',
  slug: 'prime-mover-package-2026-10-units',
  excerpt: 'Special fleet package: 10 prime movers with 0% down payment. Complete fleet financing package for large transport operators. Premium terms for bulk orders.',
  date: '2026-01-08',
  author: 'Ing Heng Credit Team',
  readTime: 6,
  category: 'Transport Vehicles',
  image: '/images/blog/prime-mover-financing.jpg'
};

const keywords = ['prime mover package', 'fleet deal', 'bulk truck financing', '0% down payment', 'transport fleet'],
  breadcrumbItems = [
  { label: 'Home', href: '/en' },
  { label: 'Blog', href: '/en/blog' },
  { label: post.title, href: `/en/blog/${post.slug}` }
];
---

<BaseLayout title={post.title} description={post.excerpt} lang={lang} keywords={keywords}>
  <script type="application/ld+json">
    {
      "@context": "https://schema.org",
      "@type": "BlogPosting",
      "headline": post.title,
      "description": post.excerpt,
      "datePublished": post.date,
      "author": { "@type": "Organization", "name": post.author },
      "publisher": {
        "@type": "Organization",
        "name": "Ing Heng Credit & Leasing Sdn Bhd",
        "logo": {
          "@type": "ImageObject",
          "url": "https://inghengcredit.com/logo.png"
        }
      }
    }
  </script>

  <Breadcrumbs items={breadcrumbItems} />

  <article class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <header class="mb-8">
      <span class="text-sm font-semibold" style="color: #D4A574;">Transport Vehicles</span>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mt-2" style="color: #2D1810; font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase;">{post.title}</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mt-4">{post.excerpt}</p>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4 text-sm text-gray-500 mt-4">
        <span>{post.author}</span>
        <span>•</span>
        <time>{new Date(post.date).toLocaleDateString('en-US', { year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric' })}</time>
        <span>•</span>
        <span>{post.readTime} min read</span>
      </div>
    </header>

    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
      <h2>10-Unit Fleet Package: Major Expansion</h2>

      <p>10 prime movers establish major transport operation. Total investment: RM1.5M-RM3.8M depending on new/used mix. Banks require RM150,000-RM760,000 down payment. Ing Heng 0% down preserves entire amount for operations.</p>

      <h2>Package Options</h2>

      <table>
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th>Package</th>
            <th>Total Value</th>
            <th>Down Payment</th>
            <th>Monthly</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <td>10 Used (RM150k each)</td>
            <td>RM1,500,000</td>
            <td>RM0</td>
            <td>~RM18,000-RM22,000</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>10 Mixed (RM200k avg)</td>
            <td>RM2,000,000</td>
            <td>RM0</td>
            <td>~RM24,000-RM29,000</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>10 New (RM380k each)</td>
            <td>RM3,800,000</td>
            <td>RM0</td>
            <td>~RM70,000-RM76,000</td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>

      <h2>10-Truck Fleet Revenue</h2>

      <h3>Monthly Earnings</h3>

      <p><strong>Normal Month:</strong>
  <br>• Revenue per truck: RM80,000
  <br>• Fleet revenue: RM800,000
  <br>• Operating costs: RM240,000
  <br>• Financing: RM20,000
  <br><strong>Net Profit: RM540,000 per month</strong></p>

      <p><strong>CNY Month:</strong>
  <br>• Fleet revenue: RM1,300,000
  <br>• Operating costs: RM300,000
  <br>• Financing: RM20,000
  <br><strong>Net Profit: RM980,000 per month</strong></p>

      <h3>First Year Revenue</h3>

      <p>Normal months (11): RM5,940,000
  <br>CNY month: RM980,000
  <br><strong>Total: RM6,920,000</strong></p>

      <h2>ROI Analysis</h2>

      <h3>10 Used Trucks (RM1.5M)</h3>

      <p><strong>Investment:</strong> RM1,500,000 (0% down)</p>

      <p><strong>First Year Profit:</strong> RM6,920,000 - RM1,500,000 = RM5,420,000</p>

      <p><strong>Payback:</strong> 2.6 months</p>

      <h3>10 New Trucks (RM3.8M)</h3>

      <p><strong>Investment:</strong> RM3,800,000 (0% down)</p>

      <p><strong>First Year Profit:</strong> RM6,920,000 - RM3,800,000 = RM3,120,000</p>

      <p><strong>Payback:</strong> 6.6 months</p>

      <h2>Package Benefits</h2>

      <ul>
        <li><strong>Volume Discount:</strong> Preferential rates for 10+ units</li>
        <li><strong>Single Financing:</strong> One approval for entire fleet</li>
        <li><strong>Staggered Deployment:</strong> Deliver trucks as you scale operations</li>
        <li><strong>Fleet Management:</strong> Optional maintenance package</li>
        <li><strong>Insurance Bundle:</strong> Group insurance rates</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Deployment Strategy</h2>

      <h3>Month 1-3: Deploy 5 Trucks</h3>
      <p>• Establish operations
  <br>• Train drivers
  <br>• Build client base</p>

      <h3>Month 4-6: Add 3 More</h3>
      <p>• Expand routes
  <br>• Increase capacity</p>

      <h3>Month 7-9: Add Final 2</h3>
      <p>• Full fleet operation
  <br>• Maximum coverage</p>

      <h2>0% Down: Cash Flow Advantage</h2>

      <p><strong>Bank 10% Down (Used Package):</strong> RM150,000</p>

      <p><strong>Ing Heng 0% Down:</strong> RM150,000 preserved</p>

      <p><strong>Use For:</strong>
  <br>• First month fuel: RM50,000
  <br>• Driver salaries: RM25,000
  <br>• Insurance: RM15,000
  <br>• Operations: RM60,000</p>

      <h2>Success Story</h2>

      <p>"Took 10-truck package in 2024. Mix of used trucks, RM1.8M total. 0% down payment saved RM180,000. Used cash for 3 months operations while building revenue. First month profit: RM420,000. Paid entire fleet in 4 months. Now generating RM500,000+ monthly pure profit. 10-truck package let me skip small fleet phase and go straight to major operation."</p>
      <p><em>— Lee Boon Siew, Transport CEO</em></p>

      <div style="background: #F5F0E8; border-left: 4px solid #D4A574; padding: 1.5rem; margin: 2rem 0;">
        <h3 style="color: #2D1810; margin-top: 0;">Get Your 10-Truck Package</h3>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 1rem;">0% down, preferential rates. Approved in 24-48 hours.</p>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 0;"><strong>Contact:</strong> +60175700889 (WhatsApp) | 03-3324 8899 (Phone)</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <footer class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t">
      <CTAButton text="Get Fleet Package Deal" link={COMPANY_INFO.whatsapp.link} variant="accent" size="large" />
    </footer>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  h2 { color: #2D1810; font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 2rem; margin-top: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; border-bottom: 3px solid #D4A574; padding-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  h3 { color: #8B6F47; font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 1.5rem; margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
  p { line-height: 1.8; color: #374151; }
  strong { color: #2D1810; font-weight: 700; }
  ul { list-style: none; padding-left: 0; }
  li { padding-left: 1.5rem; position: relative; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; line-height: 1.8; color: #374151; }
  li::before { content: '✓'; position: absolute; left: 0; color: #D4A574; font-weight: bold; }
  table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 1.5rem 0; }
  th { background: #2D1810; color: #F5F0E8; padding: 0.75rem; text-align: left; }
  td { border: 1px solid #E5E7EB; padding: 0.75rem; }
  em { display: block; margin-top: 0.5rem; color: #6B7280; font-style: normal; }
  br { display: none; }
</style>
